ter-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fthe-libertines-tickets%2Fartist%2F945319" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>购买。 </p><figure id="attachment_3809265" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3809265" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3809265" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/The-Libertines-Gunnersbury-Park-poster.-CREDIT_-Press.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="2000" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/The-Libertines-Gunnersbury-Park-poster.-CREDIT_-Press.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/The-Libertines-Gunnersbury-Park-poster.-CREDIT_-Press-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/The-Libertines-Gunnersbury-Park-poster.-CREDIT_-Press-400x400.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/The-Libertines-Gunnersbury-Park-poster.-CREDIT_-Press-800x800.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/The-Libertines-Gunnersbury-Park-poster.-CREDIT_-Press-696x696.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/The-Libertines-Gunnersbury-Park-poster.-CREDIT_-Press-1392x1392.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/The-Libertines-Gunnersbury-Park-poster.-CREDIT_-Press-1068x1068.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3809265" class="wp-caption-text">放荡者冈纳斯伯里公园的海报。图片来源：新闻界</figcaption></figure><p>Supergrass 主唱丹尼·戈菲 (Danny Goffey) 表示：“我们很高兴能与 The Libertines 和所有其他伟大乐队一起参加 Gunnersbury Park 的演出。</p><p> “古纳斯伯里公园是观看乐队表演的绝佳场所。我们第一次与 The Libertines 合作是在 22 年前的 2002 年，当时我们带着这支初出茅庐的乐队进行巡演。哇……当你玩得开心时，时间过得真快。到时见！” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="浪荡子乐队在《东方滨海艺术中心一切安静》中谈论清洁和联系" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/CtuPJQWz_mQ?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscop